    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The parts of a hat or other headgear covering the crown of the head. For head-encircling devices signifying rank or used as ornament, but not part of a hat, use "crowns (headdresses)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
